WEBVTT

01:38.160 --> 01:40.520
EPISODE 10

02:05.000 --> 02:08.800
What do you think?
I picked it out for Weiwei.

02:08.880 --> 02:12.840
- I have good taste, right?
- See? Let me take a photo.

02:12.920 --> 02:14.360
Take a photo. Come on!

02:14.560 --> 02:16.920
One, two, three!

02:22.400 --> 02:27.000
Xiaoling, can't you pick an outfit that's
more suited for a respectable woman?

02:30.880 --> 02:35.440
Miss, do you have outfits that are
more suitable for a respectable woman?

02:35.760 --> 02:37.960
Why do you think our clothes
aren't suited for respectable women?

02:38.560 --> 02:41.640
It's her problem.
She's got the hour-glass figure.

02:41.720 --> 02:42.800
So whatever she puts on...

02:47.120 --> 02:49.520
- Let's see!
- Stop it!

02:49.600 --> 02:52.360
- Let me see...
- Stop messing around.

02:53.600 --> 02:55.840
Why are you suddenly buying new clothes?

02:56.480 --> 03:00.160
Because the clothes I bought last year
have lint balls.

03:00.240 --> 03:02.640
But didn't I tell you about that ages ago?

03:02.720 --> 03:04.760
You were happy to wear them.

03:04.840 --> 03:08.120
Plus, you don't need to be shopping
right now, do you?

03:08.200 --> 03:09.800
There's an exam tomorrow.

03:12.040 --> 03:14.960
I have an important interview tomorrow.

03:15.680 --> 03:18.920
Which sick company does interviews
on a Saturday?

03:19.000 --> 03:20.760
Plus, it will be past 11,

03:20.840 --> 03:22.720
after our CET-6 exam tomorrow.

03:25.200 --> 03:27.360
For the respectable woman.

03:27.480 --> 03:29.440
- Thanks.
- Try it on.

03:31.120 --> 03:32.880
Technically, I'm not lying.

03:32.960 --> 03:36.400
Tomorrow's interview will affect
the rest of my life.

03:41.840 --> 03:42.960
Well?

03:48.080 --> 03:49.120
Applause!

03:49.840 --> 03:53.360
You've at last successfully
disguised yourself as a respectable woman.

03:54.280 --> 03:58.520
Must you be so formal, Weiwei?
Isn't it just an interview?

03:58.600 --> 04:02.440
Plus, aren't you always the one
advocating for inner beauty?

04:03.280 --> 04:07.480
For the first interview,
inner beauty doesn't matter.

04:07.640 --> 04:11.120
A heavy-grade weapon like that
should be saved as the trump card.

04:12.400 --> 04:13.440
You're unbelievable.

04:15.840 --> 04:16.839
Shoes!

04:17.399 --> 04:19.880
What's with the shoes? They look good.

04:20.959 --> 04:24.840
They'll match with a different color.

04:25.240 --> 04:26.960
- These are 37, perfect.
- No way!

04:27.040 --> 04:30.120
These don't match your outfit.
You must wear heels.

04:30.200 --> 04:32.760
That's too tall. I'm 169 cm already.

04:32.840 --> 04:35.560
Wearing these will make me 175 cm.

04:35.640 --> 04:37.840
I should wear flats. Let's see.

04:38.000 --> 04:41.560
Goodness! Why are you worried
about that for an interview?

04:41.640 --> 04:43.040
You're worried you'll be taller
than the interviewer?

04:46.320 --> 04:47.720
Exactly!

04:53.480 --> 04:57.320
What if Naihe isn't that tall?

04:59.240 --> 05:01.600
Her outfit is very conservative.

05:04.240 --> 05:07.480
Her outfit is quite refreshing
and graceful.

05:07.560 --> 05:09.240
It suits Weiwei well.

05:09.520 --> 05:13.280
If it's for an interview,
it's okay to look like a student.

05:14.120 --> 05:15.400
Come with me, to get changed.

05:21.120 --> 05:24.880
Am I the only one who finds the fully
buttoned-up collar more alluring,

05:24.960 --> 05:26.560
more seductive?

05:26.640 --> 05:30.520
That's the embodiment
of the beauty of abstinence!

05:35.480 --> 05:39.720
Weiwei is so good at bargaining.
She got a great deal for the whole outfit!

05:40.960 --> 05:44.400
I'm rather lonely
with my superb bargaining skills.

05:44.480 --> 05:47.720
Did you pick up bad habits?
You've been so narcissistic.

05:48.240 --> 05:51.400
Yes, that might be the case.

05:51.560 --> 05:53.960
One takes on the color of one's company.

05:54.040 --> 05:57.040
No, as the saying goes
lie with dogs, you're bound to get fleas.

05:57.120 --> 05:58.160
- Dogs?
- That's you!

05:58.240 --> 05:59.400
- Me?
- Doggy!

06:00.440 --> 06:03.560
Isn't that Bei Weiwei, Yiran?

06:05.160 --> 06:09.040
The shop she went to seems nice.
Let's take a look.

06:09.240 --> 06:10.120
No way.

06:10.200 --> 06:13.880
Clothes from small shops can't withstand
close inspection.

06:13.960 --> 06:18.240
Plus, however much you pay for clothes
defines your value.

06:18.320 --> 06:21.360
Since she shops there,
that's her taste-level.

06:25.880 --> 06:27.080
Yiran?

06:31.880 --> 06:34.560
What's wrong with you guys?

06:34.640 --> 06:37.200
Why do we have to wear skirts for an exam?

06:37.280 --> 06:39.200
Right after the exam, I'm going to...

06:40.560 --> 06:41.720
The interview.

06:43.040 --> 06:46.280
Weiwei rarely wears skirts.
We should coordinate our outfits.

06:46.360 --> 06:50.000
We're in different exam rooms. Why bother?

06:50.400 --> 06:52.560
It's distracting from my focus.

06:52.640 --> 06:56.080
I might start admiring myself
in the middle of the exam.

06:58.240 --> 07:00.120
You're too much.

07:00.200 --> 07:03.200
Did you catch a case of narcissism
from Weiwei?

07:03.280 --> 07:04.880
- Who are you calling a narcissist?
- You!

07:04.960 --> 07:06.520
You!

07:06.600 --> 07:08.000
We'll be late for the exam!

07:08.080 --> 07:09.040
- Hurry up!
- Come on...

07:09.120 --> 07:10.080
Hurry!

07:30.480 --> 07:32.560
Is that Bei Weiwei?

07:33.360 --> 07:35.200
She is quite pretty.

07:35.280 --> 07:37.360
Does she need to dress up
for an exam though?

07:38.040 --> 07:40.600
She's not dressed up.
She's not even wearing make-up.

07:40.680 --> 07:42.880
A pretty girl will look pretty,
even in rags.

08:24.080 --> 08:26.200
It's not even 11:10.

09:29.320 --> 09:31.040
It will be 11:30 soon.

09:31.280 --> 09:34.360
Lord is probably on his way
to Qing University.

09:34.840 --> 09:37.560
Is he as nervous as I am?

10:18.320 --> 10:19.680
Xiao Nai?

10:21.440 --> 10:25.000
Is that Xiao Nai standing
under the willow tree?

10:36.800 --> 10:41.160
It is Xiao Nai! What's he doing here?

10:41.920 --> 10:44.880
He seems to be waiting for someone, too.

10:46.680 --> 10:48.600
Who could be so lucky?

10:49.320 --> 10:51.120
Who'd Lord Xiao wait for?

10:53.760 --> 10:56.400
How come the silhouette is a bit familiar?

10:58.280 --> 10:59.880
It must be an illusion.

11:02.600 --> 11:04.720
Why does he keep looking at me?

11:05.920 --> 11:09.560
Maybe Lord Xiao Nai knows
I'm a computer major?

11:09.800 --> 11:12.040
Is that why he's looking at me?

11:14.840 --> 11:16.320
That makes more sense.

11:19.320 --> 11:22.920
Should I go say hi?

11:23.720 --> 11:25.880
We're in the same department, after all.

11:27.360 --> 11:31.960
But would he take that as a come-on?

11:46.560 --> 11:48.600
Mr. Xiao? What a coincidence!

11:51.400 --> 11:52.600
I'm so jittery.

11:52.680 --> 11:55.160
I should've just walked over.
What a terrible line.

11:55.240 --> 11:56.880
Now it's so awkward.

12:05.040 --> 12:08.920
It's not a coincidence.
I'm waiting for you.

12:16.080 --> 12:17.160
Me?

12:25.760 --> 12:26.600
Naihe?

12:27.480 --> 12:28.320
It's me.

12:32.040 --> 12:35.320
I'm so glad I didn't buy
the stiletto heels.

12:35.400 --> 12:39.080
I'm so shocked now,
I probably would've broken the heels.

12:40.680 --> 12:43.640
Naihe, Xiao Nai; Xiao Nai, Naihe.

12:43.720 --> 12:45.440
Naihe, Xiao Nai; Xiao Nai, Naihe.

12:45.520 --> 12:47.720
How did Naihe turn out to be Xiao Nai?

12:47.960 --> 12:49.400
You finished the exam early?

12:51.160 --> 12:53.080
I almost made you wait again.

12:57.280 --> 13:01.440
You mean the finals? It's fine.

13:03.960 --> 13:05.720
Is he really Naihe?

13:07.040 --> 13:09.400
Come on, let's go eat.

13:14.800 --> 13:18.280
Will another Naihe show up here later?

13:19.040 --> 13:21.320
If Xiao Nai is indeed Naihe,

13:21.600 --> 13:24.800
isn't this all too unreal?

13:31.200 --> 13:35.000
Do you eat fish, Weiwei?

13:38.600 --> 13:39.680
Weiwei?

14:00.760 --> 14:02.240
Thank you.

14:27.520 --> 14:31.160
Auntie Jiang doesn't speak,
but she's a great chef.

14:32.000 --> 14:33.520
My parents don't cook.

14:33.600 --> 14:37.120
When I was a kid, we always ate
at cafeterias or this place.

14:38.640 --> 14:40.200
When you were a kid?

14:42.520 --> 14:43.560
Would you like anything else?

14:44.800 --> 14:47.800
No, it's a huge bowl of soup.

14:47.920 --> 14:49.880
It'd be hard to finish it.

15:07.080 --> 15:08.800
Are there Chinese herbs in the soup?

15:10.320 --> 15:11.680
After my car accident,

15:11.760 --> 15:13.280
my dad ordered a half-month worth of

15:13.360 --> 15:14.800
fish head soup with Sichuan lovage rhizome
and tall gastrodia tuber,

15:14.880 --> 15:15.720
to help with my head injury.

15:21.360 --> 15:24.560
Professor Xiao?
I'm taking his elective class.

15:25.040 --> 15:26.200
Did you ever fall asleep?

15:29.080 --> 15:33.000
His lectures are a bit heady,
but they're all right.

15:33.400 --> 15:36.680
He told us about
their excavation experiences.

15:36.760 --> 15:38.320
They're interesting.

15:38.920 --> 15:42.480
I've taken his class, too.
You don't have to say nice things for him.

15:45.120 --> 15:49.280
Yeah, I sat next to you once.

15:49.720 --> 15:50.560
I know.

15:51.760 --> 15:55.000
"I know"? What does that mean?

15:57.280 --> 16:00.880
I guess for someone like Lord,
regular people's presence is mundane.

16:12.440 --> 16:17.160
Is he dumping this on me,
because he's sick of it?

16:23.120 --> 16:26.880
No way! Why would Xiao Nai and Naihe
do something so insidious?

16:26.960 --> 16:28.360
No... Never!

16:50.920 --> 16:54.480
It's so quiet. Should I talk?

16:55.440 --> 16:59.840
The Xiao Nai in front of me
is so unlike the Naihe online.

17:00.440 --> 17:05.160
He seems more distant. Forget it.

17:05.520 --> 17:08.560
I hear Xiao Nai's parents
are both from families of scholars.

17:08.880 --> 17:11.720
Maybe they have
a no-talking-while-eating rule.

17:12.240 --> 17:13.680
The more I talk, the more mistakes I make.

17:13.839 --> 17:16.480
I should save my strength for the future.

17:18.400 --> 17:22.520
That's right. Safety first.
I should just eat the fish.

17:33.680 --> 17:34.520
Have more soup.

18:32.800 --> 18:34.000
His ringtone

18:34.120 --> 18:36.000
is the "Girl Bandit Abducts Groom"
soundtrack?

18:36.080 --> 18:38.640
Does he miss being abducted?

18:39.000 --> 18:41.720
Hello? Where are you, Nai?

18:41.960 --> 18:43.560
Aren't you coming to the farewell game?

18:46.440 --> 18:48.520
Isn't it at seven? It's still early.

18:48.960 --> 18:51.680
Come soon.
Everyone's waiting for you to warm-up.

18:52.120 --> 18:54.480
What are you doing? Come over now.

18:54.640 --> 18:58.040
- I'm busy.
- Busy? Doing what?

18:58.120 --> 19:00.040
I thought you were done with work for now?

19:00.360 --> 19:02.000
- What are you doing?
- On a date.

19:03.800 --> 19:05.080
On a date?

19:06.880 --> 19:10.040
You're on a date, Nai?

19:10.560 --> 19:13.600
- Bring her...
- I'll ask her.

19:14.960 --> 19:17.720
Do you want to come to our senior class
farewell basketball game?

19:20.400 --> 19:21.360
Okay.

19:22.680 --> 19:23.640
I'll bring her in a bit.

19:26.760 --> 19:29.440
- She's coming?
- Yes.

19:30.960 --> 19:32.240
Eat up. There's no hurry.

19:35.920 --> 19:38.160
I'll go home and get my bike,
then we'll head over together.

19:41.320 --> 19:44.160
He lives around here?

20:07.400 --> 20:09.880
Lord isn't just handsome on horseback.

20:10.080 --> 20:12.240
He's handsome on a bicycle, too.

20:17.160 --> 20:18.160
Get on.

20:20.480 --> 20:25.880
Wait, this... You're taking me?

20:26.360 --> 20:29.280
Are you going to walk? It's far.

20:31.320 --> 20:33.440
You're taking me to the basketball gym?

20:33.520 --> 20:36.400
It... It's probably not the best idea?

20:36.760 --> 20:39.680
People would misread the situation.

20:41.840 --> 20:42.680
Misread?

20:43.720 --> 20:47.680
They'd think we're in that kind
of a relationship.

20:52.360 --> 20:54.960
Since when aren't we in that kind
of a relationship?

20:57.360 --> 20:58.400
I...

21:05.000 --> 21:08.200
We... When did we get in
that kind of a relationship?

21:08.320 --> 21:10.760
Even though I'd love that,

21:10.840 --> 21:13.000
but that can't be the way.

21:14.120 --> 21:15.880
On the other hand,

21:16.040 --> 21:19.000
I'd wanted to nail Lord down anyway,

21:19.160 --> 21:22.080
now that the upgraded Lord has said so,

21:22.240 --> 21:24.920
if I don't accept it,
wouldn't it be a huge loss?

21:25.520 --> 21:29.160
It'd be a loss to accept it,
it'd also be a loss not to accept it.

21:29.240 --> 21:30.800
What the heck is going on?

21:30.880 --> 21:34.280
Stop... Stop thinking...

21:34.600 --> 21:38.200
Don't fall down
the rabbit hole of his words.

21:38.360 --> 21:41.960
Pretend I didn't hear it.
Quarantine them, like viruses.

21:43.560 --> 21:45.800
Right, let's take the bike.

21:45.920 --> 21:49.280
If we walk, we'd run into more people.

21:49.520 --> 21:51.160
Biking is faster.

21:51.320 --> 21:53.920
Maybe we'll get there in no time,

21:54.000 --> 21:55.240
before anyone can make me out.

21:56.800 --> 21:57.960
I'm a good biker, you know?

21:59.760 --> 22:03.120
So, you don't have to look so...

22:04.080 --> 22:05.160
ready to embrace death.

22:10.720 --> 22:13.160
Is my expression so solemn?

23:08.920 --> 23:10.240
I need to get something.

23:15.400 --> 23:16.920
Look! He's so handsome!

23:17.480 --> 23:19.960
I like him! He's so tall.

23:20.040 --> 23:22.680
Standing next to him

23:22.760 --> 23:25.520
does draw a lot of attention.

23:34.520 --> 23:35.640
Hold this for me.

24:13.440 --> 24:14.480
Hold on tight.

24:24.960 --> 24:27.680
Maybe I should be braver.

24:28.200 --> 24:31.240
Xiao Nai... So what, if he's Xiao Nai?

24:31.520 --> 24:32.600
He's Xiao Nai in the future.

24:33.680 --> 24:37.160
Right now, he's more Naihe to me.

24:37.240 --> 24:40.840
He's just Naihe, and I like him.

24:57.360 --> 24:58.480
Wait here.

25:00.120 --> 25:03.560
There's a time and a place
for things like bravery.

25:03.720 --> 25:07.920
It's definitely not when walking
into the basketball gym with Xiao Nai,

25:08.000 --> 25:10.240
with everyone watching.

25:12.000 --> 25:15.000
I'll go watch the game with my roommates.
Let's talk online tonight.

25:43.480 --> 25:44.560
Weiwei!

25:54.960 --> 25:56.880
Go warm-up. Give your seat to Weiwei.

25:56.960 --> 25:58.440
Sure. I'll get going now.

25:58.840 --> 26:00.240
- Bye-bye!
- Bye-bye.

26:00.320 --> 26:02.200
- Bye-bye!
- Bye-bye.

26:02.880 --> 26:04.000
Here, Weiwei!

26:07.280 --> 26:09.680
Weiwei, it's really happening today.

26:10.760 --> 26:11.760
What do you mean?

26:11.840 --> 26:13.240
There are so many campus beauties here.

26:13.560 --> 26:16.720
Jiang Ruru from foreign languages,
Li Hanyu from chemistry,

26:16.800 --> 26:19.720
and the campus belle is here, too.
She's right over there.

26:20.520 --> 26:24.320
Is this the first simultaneous appearance
of top two beauties of our school?

26:24.400 --> 26:26.320
I think so.

26:26.640 --> 26:28.520
If we'd known Meng Yiran would come,

26:28.600 --> 26:30.320
you could've worn that red dress,
Weiwei.

26:30.640 --> 26:33.040
You totally would've crushed her, okay?

26:33.120 --> 26:35.840
That's right. Meng Yiran's figure

26:35.920 --> 26:38.120
has nothing on our Weiwei.

26:38.200 --> 26:41.680
Weiwei's face is much prettier, too.

26:42.120 --> 26:45.080
Who took that photo of Weiwei
for the contest last year?

26:45.160 --> 26:47.000
It was a terrible picture.

26:47.240 --> 26:50.680
She was disadvantaged,
compared to Meng Yiran's close-up photo.

26:50.960 --> 26:53.640
I know! Weiwei wouldn't let us
upload a nicer photo.

26:53.720 --> 26:55.360
- She should've taken more photos.
- Right?

26:56.640 --> 26:58.280
Let's eat...

26:58.840 --> 26:59.880
Did you hit the jackpot, Weiwei?

26:59.960 --> 27:01.920
Snacks galore! How much was everything?

27:02.000 --> 27:03.560
I want this.

27:04.680 --> 27:08.120
- You got my favorite dried mango!
- And roasted cashew nuts!

27:08.200 --> 27:12.480
Why didn't you get my favorite
pecans, Weiwei?

27:13.320 --> 27:16.800
- You're being picky now?
- No, I'm sorry.

27:19.360 --> 27:21.560
Lord stuffed a huge bag in three minutes.

27:21.640 --> 27:23.080
You're expecting variety from him?

27:23.560 --> 27:27.120
Did you get the job, Weiwei?
So you bought snacks to celebrate?

27:29.560 --> 27:30.480
You could say that.

27:31.080 --> 27:33.000
How was the interview?

27:34.040 --> 27:37.680
Well... The process was rather
disappointing, but the end was surprising.

27:38.400 --> 27:41.240
Who cares if it's surprising,
as long as you got the job?

27:43.880 --> 27:46.240
By the way, Weiwei,
what matters the most,

27:46.320 --> 27:49.040
is that Lord Xiao Nai will definitely
be here today!

27:51.000 --> 27:52.880
I know he's coming, of course.

27:52.960 --> 27:55.080
You're eating the snacks he bought.

27:55.160 --> 27:58.880
Say, today's game is between
computer and architecture departments.

27:58.960 --> 28:01.440
Meng Yiran isn't in our department.
What's she doing here?

28:01.760 --> 28:03.720
You can't say that, Sisi.

28:03.840 --> 28:06.120
Handsome men are a shared resource
for all people.

28:06.200 --> 28:07.760
You can't have prejudice in that regard.

28:08.800 --> 28:10.960
Look... What did I tell you?

28:11.040 --> 28:12.480
Bei Weiwei would show up for sure.

28:12.720 --> 28:15.240
Why would a girl like her
give up such an opportunity?

28:21.600 --> 28:23.920
- The cashews are good.
- I want some.

28:24.000 --> 28:25.440
Don't finish them yourself!

28:25.520 --> 28:28.240
You're eating so fast. Come on!

29:23.360 --> 29:24.560
Everyone, please.

29:24.640 --> 29:26.280
Hurry and return to your seats.

29:26.360 --> 29:29.640
Come on... Get a move on!
Hurry, let's go...

29:31.640 --> 29:33.640
Nai, what are you doing here?

29:33.720 --> 29:34.640
Where is she?

29:38.440 --> 29:39.720
Where's your date?

29:40.160 --> 29:43.280
Right. I texted Hao Mei
and asked him to come.

29:43.520 --> 29:44.520
Ran off.

29:44.960 --> 29:46.400
- Ran off?
- Ran off?

29:47.280 --> 29:48.160
You guys scared her off.

29:50.760 --> 29:53.240
I'm so cute. Who would I scare off?

29:54.640 --> 29:58.840
They're probably the two guys
who called him on the phone.

29:59.240 --> 30:02.200
Are they Yugong and Houzi Jiu?

30:02.520 --> 30:04.080
Okay, let's go change.

30:08.120 --> 30:11.000
Yiran, Xiao Nai was looking at you.

30:11.760 --> 30:14.720
Could it be? There are so many people.

30:14.800 --> 30:16.440
Please! These people here

30:16.520 --> 30:18.160
are just the background for you, okay?

30:18.240 --> 30:21.040
Didn't you meet Xiao Nai
at your uncle's office?

30:21.120 --> 30:22.560
I'm sure he remembers you.

30:23.480 --> 30:25.600
Bei Weiwei sat through a class with him,

30:25.680 --> 30:28.000
but they never spoke. Right?

30:29.000 --> 30:31.440
Say, who was Xiao Nai looking at?

30:32.080 --> 30:32.920
Probably Meng Yiran?

30:33.280 --> 30:36.200
Not necessarily.
There are many pretty girls here today.

30:37.480 --> 30:40.760
But Xiao Nai was looking in our direction.

30:40.840 --> 30:43.280
That could only be Meng Yiran.

30:43.760 --> 30:48.480
I remember now! Maybe Xiao Nai
and Meng Yiran know each other.

30:49.720 --> 30:52.360
The only time Xiao Nai participated
in the school gala,

30:52.440 --> 30:54.080
Meng Yiran performed on stage, too.

30:54.160 --> 30:56.280
They didn't perform together,

30:56.600 --> 30:59.080
but they both performed
folk instruments.

30:59.160 --> 31:00.480
Maybe they crossed paths.

31:01.960 --> 31:04.440
Maybe Xiao Nai wasn't looking at a girl.

31:04.520 --> 31:06.360
Why do you have to think him so shallow?

31:07.280 --> 31:09.400
Please! Don't be so naive.

31:09.480 --> 31:11.560
When has Xiao Nai ever looked up
at the bleachers?

31:11.640 --> 31:13.640
He always treats people like thin air.

31:15.160 --> 31:17.360
He must have been looking at someone.

31:17.840 --> 31:19.200
There is only one truth.

31:21.720 --> 31:25.280
He was looking at... me.

31:36.480 --> 31:37.840
- Let's head out.
- Go!

31:37.920 --> 31:41.480
- Coming...
- Break a leg...

31:41.560 --> 31:44.760
Mr. Hou, I saw Nai looking up
at the bleachers earlier.

31:44.840 --> 31:47.040
Something's fishy.

31:47.520 --> 31:50.760
This is the first time
I find your logic to be impeccable.

31:58.160 --> 32:00.880
Look at Nai,
he's already got a handsome face,

32:00.960 --> 32:02.320
and he's got a nice body!

32:02.760 --> 32:05.200
Don't change the subject.

32:05.280 --> 32:08.040
Come on, Nai, who were you looking at?

32:08.320 --> 32:09.760
Which pretty girl?

32:09.840 --> 32:13.160
I noticed that line of vision included
our campus belle.

32:13.640 --> 32:16.000
And the department belle,
whom I keep running into.

32:17.400 --> 32:20.480
I told you,
it's got nothing to do with you.

32:20.560 --> 32:23.160
You'd better explain yourself.

32:23.680 --> 32:27.160
Hey, you just recovered from your injury.
Are you sure you can play ball?

32:27.400 --> 32:29.160
I'm fine. Don't worry.

32:29.600 --> 32:31.200
Come on, get changed.

32:34.600 --> 32:35.960
Weiwei,

32:36.040 --> 32:40.880
don't you know you and Xiao Nai are
recognized as the least likely couple?

32:42.560 --> 32:44.440
Recognized as the least likely couple?

32:44.520 --> 32:47.440
It's a popular gossip forum.

32:47.520 --> 32:50.920
It paired up all the famous
single students on campus.

32:51.160 --> 32:53.560
You and Xiao Nai are the least compatible.

32:54.240 --> 32:56.360
Why do they have forums like that?

32:56.720 --> 32:58.840
- These people have too much free time.
- Xiaoling!

32:58.920 --> 33:00.640
I forgot to do my homework.

33:00.720 --> 33:02.640
Did you do it? Can I see it?

33:03.400 --> 33:05.360
Why aren't we compatible?

33:05.880 --> 33:09.200
Why are you taking such vain things
so seriously, Weiwei?

33:09.880 --> 33:12.240
According to the forum comments,

33:12.320 --> 33:14.360
it's because of looks, occupations...

33:15.560 --> 33:17.560
How did they put it? Let me think.

33:18.120 --> 33:18.960
I got it!

33:19.280 --> 33:24.840
They said, "One is elegant and light
like an ink wash painting.

33:25.040 --> 33:28.000
The other is colorful and heavy,
like an oil painting.

33:28.080 --> 33:30.280
One is a celestial being of another world.

33:30.360 --> 33:32.920
The other is an adenium flower
on rustic earth."

33:34.760 --> 33:37.760
- What's that look on your face?
- I got goose bumps.

33:37.840 --> 33:40.520
Also, I'm not oily at all. Okay?

33:41.680 --> 33:43.240
That's a bad joke.

33:44.720 --> 33:46.520
Why aren't our occupations compatible?

33:46.600 --> 33:50.000
We're both computer majors.
We should be known as the "Techy Couple."

33:51.840 --> 33:52.880
Why are you laughing?

33:52.960 --> 33:55.280
Can you come up with a worse name?

33:55.760 --> 33:59.160
When you're in the same field,
there's no sense of idolization, okay?

33:59.560 --> 34:03.520
Plus, computers are only one
of Xiao Nai's strengths.

34:08.719 --> 34:11.639
Tell me, who did they say
was compatible with Xiao Nai?

34:12.560 --> 34:15.520
No one. They couldn't reach a consensus.

34:16.159 --> 34:17.679
See?

34:25.480 --> 34:26.360
They're out!

34:26.880 --> 34:30.440
Xiao Nai...

34:32.719 --> 34:36.040
Go...

34:53.000 --> 34:56.080
Xiao Nai is everyone's idol.

34:56.159 --> 34:59.400
Say, Xiao Nai is a better swimmer
than basketball player.

34:59.480 --> 35:03.360
I wonder what he looks like
during a swim meet?

35:18.200 --> 35:20.600
Why is your face so hot, Weiwei?

35:24.800 --> 35:26.680
- Your thoughts are impure!
- Me?

35:26.760 --> 35:28.880
- Your thoughts are impure.
- Your thoughts are impure.

35:28.960 --> 35:30.720
I think I've been wrongly accused.

35:30.800 --> 35:32.200
- You have impure thoughts, too!
- You, too!

35:32.280 --> 35:33.520
- You, too!
- Who?

35:33.600 --> 35:35.080
The game's starting.

36:16.960 --> 36:18.240
FIRST QUARTER
COMPUTER VS. ARCHITECTURE

36:55.840 --> 36:57.160
Nice job, everyone.

36:57.520 --> 36:58.920
- Later...
- Yes?

36:59.000 --> 37:00.680
- We can pick up the pace.
- Okay.

37:00.760 --> 37:03.040
- Dazhong, you're on rebounds.
- Got it.

37:03.120 --> 37:05.200
Houzi, cover more positions.

37:05.400 --> 37:07.440
Particularly on defense, you can do more.

37:07.520 --> 37:08.720
Okay.

37:09.800 --> 37:13.520
Xiao Nai's mid-air direction change
was so awesome!

37:13.600 --> 37:15.600
I'll ask Dazhong to work on it.

37:15.920 --> 37:18.880
I think he needs to be very fit.

37:18.960 --> 37:20.320
I don't know.

37:21.720 --> 37:24.000
Xiao Nai is a master
of both pen and sword.

37:25.680 --> 37:28.120
He's such a quality person.

37:28.480 --> 37:30.360
If we do end up together,

37:30.520 --> 37:32.600
I'll have to work harder.

37:49.320 --> 37:50.960
SECOND QUARTER
COMPUTER VS. ARCHITECTURE

38:45.840 --> 38:48.520
THIRD QUARTER
COMPUTER VS. ARCHITECTURE

38:56.960 --> 38:58.640
- Take over my position later.
- Okay.

39:02.880 --> 39:04.680
Dazhong was right.

39:04.760 --> 39:07.520
Xiao Nai is only playing half of the game.

39:07.600 --> 39:08.920
Why's that?

39:09.440 --> 39:10.760
It's the farewell game.

39:10.840 --> 39:13.440
Bench players get floor time, too.

39:15.920 --> 39:20.520
I heard Xiao Nai
was in a car accident recently.

39:20.600 --> 39:21.600
Car accident?

39:22.800 --> 39:26.160
It's not good for him
to exercise for too long, right?

39:26.880 --> 39:28.680
How did I forget that?

39:28.760 --> 39:30.480
Why is he still on the court?

39:31.040 --> 39:32.080
What did you forget?

39:33.920 --> 39:34.880
Nothing.

40:41.600 --> 40:43.320
The team is going out later.

40:43.480 --> 40:46.720
I might not be able to go online tonight.
What are you doing tomorrow?

40:49.080 --> 40:51.240
- Study.
- Okay. I'll go with you.

40:53.120 --> 40:55.880
Okay, I'll save you a seat.

40:58.280 --> 41:00.800
There's an empty seat.
Will you scoot over?

41:12.400 --> 41:13.720
What's going on?

43:52.280 --> 43:54.720
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
